                <listAnnotation xml:lang="en" type="notes">
                    
                        <note n="1" xml:id="note-t-1">
                            
                    
<p>The Salon opened on 1 May.</p>
                        </note>
                        
                    
                        <note n="2" xml:id="note-t-2">
                            
                    
<p>That Van Gogh had indeed sent this (lost) letter is confirmed by <ref xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" target="let341.xml#l-144">letter 341, ll. 144-146</ref>, in which he thanks <rs xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" type="person" ref="bio.xml#_1306">Van Rappard</rs> for his promise by telegram. </p>
                        </note>
                        
                            

                        
                    
